title: Atomic Kitten - So Far So Good [2001] DVD5
description: Atomic Kitten - So Far So Good [2001] DVD5 So Far So Good is the first DVD by Atomic Kitten and was released in 2001. It is also available as video. It is also the only DVD which features Kerry Katona before she left the band due to her pregnancy. The video consists of interviews and footage of the promotion tours, the first big concert in Liverpool. The majority of the footage was created using handheld cameras. It also contains the music videos for "Right Now", "See Ya", "I Want Your Love", "Follow Me", "Whole Again" and two versions of "Eternal Flame" Year of manufacture: 2001 Country: United Kingdom Genre: Pop Duration: 1:07:26 Label: Virgin/Universal/Innocent ?
